    "This era witnessed the advent of electronic accounting for deposit, remittance, and loan transactions, alongside advancements in infrastructure such as magnetic stripe credit card technology, ATMs, and POS machines, significantly enhancing data processing capabilities and financial service efficiency.",
    "In the subsequent stage of Internet + finance, internet technology expanded the horizons of financial transactions, while big data and cloud computing bolstered business efficiency.",
    "Services like online banking, mobile banking, cardless payments, internet-based credit facilities, and personal finance services emerged, catalyzing the convergence of finance and technology.",
